<br>
Stand close get in the mob's face.<br>
<br>
I believe Dalninil is referring to the Short sword of veridix. A little slow for my taste, and drops in Veeshan's Peak, proc is nice though. I have one, but prefer the Frostbringer for now as the debuff seems to pull agro for me better. But it comes down to preferance. They dont call Dalninil's sword the &quot;Mini SoD&quot; on other servers for nothing.<br>
<br>
Dont forget pure DPS. Haste and a pair of fast swords, seem to work fine. I have used a pair of banked Lammies on CR and have had no trouble holding agro.<br>
<br>
If your not on OT faction, go to Howling stones and snag a bloodpoint.<br>
<br>
Tribulation is WW dragon capable I think, grab a dragon head, do the Frostbringer quest.<br>
<br>
Dont laugh, the little 8 - 22 Praetor's blade of debility, pulls incredible agro. Easy Luclin Quest blade. Sells for 250 pp in the Bazaar.<br>
<br>
Ornate sword of the General, 10 18 with nice stats. Nice Mainhand weapon.<br>
<br>
Wavecrasher from Siren's Grotto, excellent taunting 1 hander. 9 - 19 with I believe 20 percent slow, 200 dot proc.<br>
<br>
Hope that helps. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://pub33.ezboard.com/bleagueofshadows"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.yahara.net/fortim/Dvara.jpg"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><br>
